## Kelly Criterion Sizing: Bet Like a Pro

**Formula**:  
`Bet Size = (b × p - q) / b × f × Bankroll`

| Profile | Kelly Fraction | Max Bet |
|--------|----------------|---------|
| **Conservative** | 1/10 | **0.5%** |
| **Balanced** | 1/4 | **1.2%** |
| **Aggressive** | 1/2 | **2.5%** |

**Example**: $10,000 bankroll, Q3 Reversal at +140 (55.3% prob)  
- **Balanced**: **$120 bet** (1.2%)

